  <description><![CDATA[<p>The superior Lion Bansko ensures high standards throughout. Designed in a smart contemporary style, hotel's informal and relaxed ambience combined with extensive leisure facilities are ideal for unwinding after a day on the slopes. The hotel is a firm favourite with Ingham's guests.</p>
<p><strong>Location: </strong>The main gondola station is approximately 6 minutes’ walk (600m) away and the hotel’s own shuttle service also runs regularly throughout the day.</p>]]></description>
